    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Call up your buddies and enjoy the acidic chaos of Citrus Rampage, a physics-based multiplayer shooter with silly guns and destructible environments. Play with up to 4 players in local multiplayer or online using Steam Remote Play Together. Your friends don’t need to own the game to play online with you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817020/extras/c5e9408c75d43954c235931ef25f2829.poster.avif?t=1750611178\" width=600 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817020/extras/c5e9408c75d43954c235931ef25f2829.webm?t=1750611178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A CORROSIVE ARSENAL</h2>Shoot your enemies with the gatling gun, blow them up with fireworks, scare them with the chicken gun, knock them down using the banana gun and much more! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLODE AND SMASH</h2>Use physics-based havoc to kill enemies as you destroy the surrounding environment. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WATCH YOUR STEP</h2>Avoid traps or trigger them intentionally to surprise and eliminate your opponents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENHANCE YOUR POWER</h2>Collect power ups to become invulnerable, to change the flow of time, or to run faster to beat your opponents. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNIQUE GAME MODES</h2>Play the classic Team Deathmatch and Capture The Flag, enjoy the funny Kick and Kill soccer mode or prove you are the best volleyball player! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Citrus Rampage is now sharing channels with the official Duck Game Discord server! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
